{"tid":247813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為認叻胸襲女同學估cup數    理大男生判感化1年","createTime":"2017-05-18T05:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T11:07:40.000Z","uid":48093,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ce846e9835fe458d6f40f685858ae95e1a941c","tid":247813,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:54:44.000Z","msg":"由副學士轉輾升讀學士課程的理工大學男生，稱因年紀比同學大，為了認叻及得到認為，與迎新營新相識同學到網吧打機時，向19歲女同學自誇「一手揸落去就知乜cup數」，同時出手揑她的乳房，並問女生「係咪A cup尾至B cup呀？」男生早前承認非禮罪，今判感化1年。<br />\n<br />\n男被告張鴻浩（22歲）去年8月6日在旺角一間網吧內，獲5名教授寫信為他求情。裁判官引述感化報告指被告表露悔意，裁判官亦認為被告已上了寶貴一課，希望他汲取教訓。<br />\n同案涉有樣學樣、跟隨被告胸襲女事主的另一男被告陳裕恒（21歲）則獲准保釋，本月24日判刑。"},{"pid":"5ca8711a95474562f5d28924b0f543b251b18843","tid":247813,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:55:36.000Z","msg":"B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c89fef0aeab6343c5f4a831b3ffe5d5d46389df","tid":247813,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:55:55.000Z","msg":"一左一右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd8167ec136ab3620a015f7d5f3b1f549962eb4","tid":247813,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:56:23.000Z","msg":"留名睇 勞資糾紛"},{"pid":"a8c75f7d5af1119cbd3ea41aa3419f5fc6596151","tid":247813,"uid":50789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"落鳩我面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  告鳩你條撚屌先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d63ea87060e164aa762f4249d8c1199f7c29cc","tid":247813,"uid":74155,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:09:57.000Z","msg":"可能估唔啱cup樓先畀人告呢"},{"pid":"7244677d94f018ec2341b91d02d4e87cce698fdb","tid":247813,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06: